original_title: Shaawanoki: The Mystery of the Swamp Apes
overview: Ronnie Roseman, Andreas Wallach, and Peter Byrne document the history and notoriety of the Florida Bigfoot also known as the ‘Skunk Ape.’ Is Shaawanoki (its Native American name), the Florida version of the legendary Bigfoot of the Pacific Northwest? You may find your answer by watching, SHAAWANOKI – The ‘Skunk Ape’, Florida’s Bigfoot.
title: Shaawanoki: The Mystery of the Swamp Apes
